Insider Activity


Individual




Michael J. Hartnett



Dr. Michael J. Hartnett is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at RBC Bearings, Inc. and President & Chief Executive Officer at Roller Bearing Co. of America, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Process Fab, Inc. and Leading Edge Aviation Services, Inc.
Dr. Hartnett was previously employed as President & General Manager by Industrial Tectonics Bearings Corp. and Vice President & GM-Aerospace Business Unit by Timken US Corp. He also served on the board at ATC Technology Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of New Haven, a graduate degree from Worcester Polytechnic Institute, and a doctorate degree from the University of Connecticut.



